Justification for Job Requisition – Model Developer Replacement

The replacement of the Model Developer is critical to ensure continuity in maintaining and delivering fraud detection models. This role is essential to meeting stakeholder commitments, keeping models accurate and compliant, and responding quickly to emerging fraud risks. Without timely replacement, we face delays in delivery, reduced detection capability, and increased operational and financial risk.


